# Nook and Care — Agent Rules

## What This Project Is

**Nook and Care** (`find-your-nook.base44.app`) is a **senior housing marketplace platform** helping families find verified senior care facilities. It is built with **Next.js 14** (App Router), **TypeScript**, and **Tailwind CSS**.

The platform serves:
- **Families / Seniors** — search, compare, tour-book facilities
- **Housing Providers** — list, manage, and showcase their facilities
- **Agents** — access leads and premium data
- **Platform Administrators** — verify listings and manage the marketplace

