## Design System

### Colors (Tailwind)
- **Primary:** `teal-600` (#0d9488) — buttons, badges, links, accents
- **Primary hover:** `teal-700` (#0f766e)
- **Background:** `white` / `slate-50` / `teal-50`
- **Footer background:** `slate-900` (#0f172a)
- **Text:** `slate-900` headings, `slate-600` body, `slate-400` muted
- **Warning/Urgent:** `amber-400` / `yellow-400` banner

### Typography
- Headings: `font-bold` or `font-semibold`, `text-slate-900`
- Body: `text-slate-600`, `leading-relaxed`
- Links: `text-teal-600 hover:text-teal-700`

### Components
- Buttons (primary): `bg-teal-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-teal-700 transition-colors`
- Cards: `bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow`
- Badges: `bg-teal-600 text-white text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full`

